## Detailed Implementation Plan: `Bun.INI` Namespace

### Overview

This plan adds a `Bun.INI` namespace with `parse` and `stringify` methods, following the exact same registration pattern as `Bun.TOML`, `Bun.YAML`, `Bun.JSON5`, and `Bun.JSONC`. The INI parser and stringifier will be self-contained within a single new file, `INIObject.zig`, avoiding reuse of `src/ini.zig` (which is tightly coupled with environment variable substitution and npmrc-specific logic).

